function updateSelfSignedJwtStubs() {

savedProto = {} savedProto._getDateNow = SelfSignedJwt._getDateNow savedProto._getNewJwtId = SelfSignedJwt._getNewJwtId

SelfSignedJwt.prototype._getDateNow = function() { return cp[‘nowDate’] } SelfSignedJwt.prototype._getNewJwtId = function() { return cp[‘jwtId’] }

return savedProto

}
